{"tid":953330,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"商務部指中美經貿磋商取得新進展","createTime":"2018-12-24T00:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T01:50:02.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d57c7e18b60b6a7bce3f3c83bfe5617e00bfb34","tid":953330,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=331794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331794&d=JcB2XAMnINmnq8cHyxjvOtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=703740af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331794&h=f66db52d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=331794</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地計劃訂立外國投資法，加強保護外商的合法權益。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會審議了外商投資法草案，加強保護外商的合法權益。草案訂明要建立高水平投資自由化便利化政策，建立和完善外商投資促進機制，營造穩定、透明及可預期的投資環境，外商投資企業可以依法通過公開發行股票、公司債券或其他方式融資。<br />\n<br />\n草案又提出多項措施保障外商權益，包括不得利用行政手段強制轉讓技術、依法平等保護知識產權、各級政府及相關部門不得違法設置市場准入及退出條件、違法干預外商投資企業的正常經營活動，同時要完善外商投資企業的投訴維權機制。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe3b4832a0cde88fa77d43dc7cb0a5ad334c2aa","tid":953330,"uid":13008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d57c7e18b60b6a7bce3f3c83bfe5617e00bfb34","tid":953330,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=331794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331794&d=JcB2XAMnINmnq8cHyxjvOtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=703740af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331794&h=f66db52d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">